text: The Tenasserim lutung (Trachypithecus barbei) is a species of lutung. It is found in Myanmar and Thailand. It is named after the Tenasserim Hills. ==References== Tenasserim lutung Category:Primates of Southeast Asia Category:Mammals of Myanmar Category:Mammals of Thailand Tenasserim lutung Category:Tenasserim Hills
title: Tenasserim lutung
